data.description: 706 Jane Way is the whole package and more with no HOA. Centrally located to Hospital, town, schools, shops, Military bases and easy access to Spanish Moss Trail. Upgrades detailed in private remarks. You will adore your coastal home over looking your neighborhood duck pond out front and walk out patio and deck over looking fenced in backyard with fire pit, active garden, playground and beautiful live oak. Kitchen features double ovens, plenty of cabinet space and granite countertops. 2 nice living room spaces one with relaxing fireplace and primary suite on the first floor. Solar panels will keep those electric bills low and Green living. Closet have builtins for plenty of storage. Large windows allow lots of natural light and view of pond from upper living room.  Love where you live
